layout.message: Make sure that you have the correct layout turned on.

page_action_help.message:
Use SuperGenPass easily!

Click on your password. If your password is locked, enter it to unlock.

Click on ‘...’ to use a new password.

Click on domain to change it.

Click on  to fill the page with generated password.
